Signup model validations:
- first name
  - must be present and must only contain letters, spaces, apostrophes and hyphens
  - limited to 96 chars
- last name
  - must be present and must only contain letters, spaces, apostrophes and hyphens
  - limited to 96 chars
- email
  - must be present and must pass email validation for format
  - limited to 64 chars
- phone number
  - must be present and must be at least 10 chars in NA, 5 in EU
- password
  - must be present
  - between 6 and 40 chars
